
 <h2>Welcome to Datspleef!</h2> 
 
 <h5>It's kind of like <a href="http://www.datpiff.com"> Datpiff</a></h5>
 
 <p>
 	Our website is a convenient way to share and listen to mixtapes. Users can add artists, and then add those artists' mixtapes. 
 	When looking at the list of artists, clicking "See Artist" shows all of that artist's mixtapes.
 	Lists of mixtapes are always sorted by their number of listens.
 </p>
 <p>
			<a href="#" id="show" class="styledHelp">Show Help</a>
			<a href="#" id="hide" class="styledHelp">Hide Help</a>
</p>

